snippet.title: Shining Stars 3: Sanctuary of the Star Comet Preview 3 - Snowflower View
snippet.description:
Hi guys! This is the 3rd preview of SS3, Snowflower View! This is the 3rd course of the game. Mario visits the 4th wonder of the world, Snowflower View! This area is part of the Sanctuary of Ice, as shown by the symbols around the level. You can see many skeeters, chuckyas and other enemies here, as well as meet with one of the Doll Magician's dolls herself!
